rComments: She is one of the best professors I have ever had. Her experience in the field shows in her lectures and her explanations. I have taken her courses since my undergrad and glad to continue to have her in grad school. Marci is an inspiration to what I can become and who I want to be.
Very helpful, clear, and cares about her students inside and outside of class. One of my favorite instructors throughout college.
She's extremely helpful and wants everyone to do well. Be prepared to write tons of notes everyday.
